UNITED STATES of America ex rel. LEUNG FOOK, Next Friend and Father of Leung Chee Dai, Appellant, v. Rudolph REIMER, Director of Immigration and Naturalization at the Port of New York, Appellee. No. 36. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Oct. 30, 1939. James C. Thomas, of New York City, for appellant. John T. Cahill, U. S. Atty., of New York City (Ambrose J. Delehanty, Asst. U. S. Atty., of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before L. HAND, SWAN, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed on authority of United States ex rel. Fong Lung Sing v. Day, 2 Cir., 37 F.2d 36.
